text.section:
The cabinet shall promulgate regulations governing loans made under KRS 183.200 to 183.210. The regulations shall provide:
The rate of interest to be charged;
The terms of the loans;
Standards for determining the soundness and feasibility of projects;
The form and contents of applications for loans; and
Such other matters as the secretary may determine to be necessary consistent with the provisions of KRS 183.200 to 183.210.
